</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Anthony Williams, 56, assistant director of finance at Scotland Yard, will
appear before magistrates today on two charges of theft from the
Metropolitan Police involving more than Pounds 30,000. Mr Williams had
earlier been arrested by detectives investigating the disappearance of more
than Pounds 4m from police funds.
